reagent-name-antihol = antihol
reagent-desc-antihol = Rapidly purges alcohol and helps clear light poisoning from the bloodstream.

reagent-name-spaceacillin = spaceacillin
reagent-desc-spaceacillin = A spacefaring antibiotic. In this build it mainly serves as a core os_chem component and antiseptic.

reagent-name-atropine = atropine
reagent-desc-atropine = A critical stabilizer for dying patients. Handles severe airloss and helps keep someone alive on the edge of death, but punishes careless use.

reagent-name-liquid-solder = liquid solder
reagent-desc-liquid-solder = A metallic repair solution for delicate electronics and positronic brains.

reagent-name-salicylic-acid = salicylic acid
reagent-desc-salicylic-acid = A light analgesic and brute-treatment aid. Also cools down an overheated patient.

reagent-name-salbutamol = salbutamol
reagent-desc-salbutamol = A strong anti-asphyxiation medicine that lets a patient survive without air for much longer.

reagent-name-anti-burn-stimulant = anti-burn stimulant
reagent-desc-anti-burn-stimulant = A specialized burn treatment. Stimulates the recovery of damaged tissue.

reagent-name-silver-sulfadiazine = silver sulfadiazine
reagent-desc-silver-sulfadiazine = A contact treatment for burns. It works best when applied externally.

reagent-name-styptic-powder = styptic powder
reagent-desc-styptic-powder = A contact treatment for brute damage. It rapidly seals external wounds.

reagent-name-synthflesh = synthflesh
reagent-desc-synthflesh = Synthetic tissue paste for external treatment of both brute and burn damage.

reagent-name-syntmorphine = syntmorphine
reagent-desc-syntmorphine = A powerful analgesic. It numbs pain, but buildup causes drowsiness and narcotic sleep.

reagent-name-pentetic-acid = pentetic acid
reagent-desc-pentetic-acid = An aggressive blood cleanser for toxins and radiation. Very useful, but rough on the body.

reagent-name-perfluorodecalin = perfluorodecalin
reagent-desc-perfluorodecalin = One of the strongest medicines against asphyxiation. It buys precious time in the worst situations.

reagent-name-rezadone = rezadone
reagent-desc-rezadone = A restorative medicine for severe tissue and cellular damage, including mangled facial tissue.

reagent-name-mutadone = mutadone
reagent-desc-mutadone = Restores genetics back to baseline and removes jittering.

reagent-name-calomel = calomel
reagent-desc-calomel = Rapidly flushes chemicals from the bloodstream, but is dangerous for patients who are otherwise stable.

reagent-name-ether = ether
reagent-desc-ether = A sedative that gradually puts the patient to sleep.

reagent-name-fomepizole = fomepizole
reagent-desc-fomepizole = Knocks down severe drunkenness and calms the nerves.

reagent-name-teporone = teporone
reagent-desc-teporone = Pushes body temperature back toward normal by heating or cooling as needed.

reagent-name-acetaldehyde = acetaldehyde
reagent-desc-acetaldehyde = A vinegar aldehyde and an intermediate component for more advanced os_chem recipes.

reagent-name-formaldehyde = formaldehyde
reagent-desc-formaldehyde = A toxic preservative and an important intermediate for medical and toxic chemistry.

reagent-name-acetic-acid = acetic acid
reagent-desc-acetic-acid = An acidic intermediate reagent for advanced pharmacology and food chemistry.